    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "If I understand the protocol correctly, friend requests have onion routing enabled. A friend request can also have a piece of text attached to it.\r\n\r\nSo like, can't we enable full onion routing with this design? That is, to send every message with onion routing.",
